---
/* Brief 70c §2 — Testnet disclaimer banner shown on home + dashboard.
   Positioned below SiteHeader, above the main content. */
---

<div class="border-y border-pos/25 bg-pos/[0.06]">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 sm:px-6">
    <span class="inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-pos
                 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(134,239,172,0.7)]"></span>
    <p class="text-[12.5px] leading-[1.5] text-text sm:text-[13px]">
      <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-pos">
        Live on Binance Testnet
      </span>
      <span class="text-text-dim"> — Real orders, simulated money. Every trade
        you see is executed on Binance's test exchange.
        The logic is real, the dollars aren't. Yet.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
